properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 6 at 3:55PM EST until February 7 at 1:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Gale Warning, south winds 25 to 30 kt with gusts
up to 40 kt. For the Small Craft Advisory, south winds 20 to 25
kt with gusts up to 35 kt expected. Bay waters 2 to 4 feet and
very rough.

* WHERE...Tampa Bay waters.

* WHEN...For the Gale Warning, until 1 AM EST Friday. For the
Small Craft Advisory, from 1 AM to 10 AM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 AM EST FRIDAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM TO 10 AM EST FRIDAY
